divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving back from northern California on Hwy 395, my friend and I noticed some strange colored clouds and he decided to take pictures of the clouds. While we were reviewing them to see if they turned out, we came across one photo that captured something that we had not seen while taking the pictures. We don't know what it is and never acutally saw it with our own eyes but it turned up on the photograph.
